          "kdqol36_mh_grid_2",
          "kdqol36_mh_grid_3"
        ],
        "description": "SF-12 Physical Component Summary (PCS). Computed from relevant SF-12 items using the SF-12 scoring algorithm (Ware et al., 1996). Score is standardized to a mean of 50 (SD=10).",
